+### Release route help and invalid-argument safety
+
+`./ns release-prep --help`, `./ns release-gate --help`, `./ns release-publish --help`, and `./ns release-verify --help` must be read-only. Help output, invalid arguments, and invalid versions must not create branches, tags, releases, commits, files, or dirty working trees.
